# Ignore symlinked shared skills (generated by sync-skills.sh)
*
!.gitignore

# Whitelist project-authored skills below. For each real directory under
# .claude/skills/ that belongs to this project (not a generated symlink),
# add a pair of entries using its actual directory name. For example, if
# you have .claude/skills/my-local-skill/, uncomment and rename these:
# !my-local-skill/
# !my-local-skill/**
